    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192880/extras/0bf2f18a7f4a27dd7abc14eb84470f4d.apng?t=1763996276\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192880/extras/0bf2f18a7f4a27dd7abc14eb84470f4d.poster.avif?t=1763996276\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=225 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is an indie, passion-project single-player survival RTS game designed to put the player's species on a foreign and hostile land, and let the player lead them from humble beginnings to an eventual complete exploitation of an unknown world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have to find said planet to populate. Though, you should be wary of the space anomalies occupying specific planets and solar systems. After descending to a planet's surface, your objective becomes to find a way to brave this new world, teeming with alien life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources like wood, stone and food. Eventually, you might even find a way to refine them into something more precious?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore different biomes, lead expeditions into ruins or even wilder parts of the planet!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build, develop and expand your colony to prosper.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to lead your species to new frontiers?</p>",
